             sworn.</p>
               <p>I found these halfpence on the prisoner.</p>
               <p>(The halfpence produced and deposed to by the prosecutor.)</p>
               <p>Prosecutor. Those halfpence that are here I marked twenty-four by the letter of the alphabet, and some by numbers, those which I found on the prisoner correspond with the nine missed.</p>
               <p>The prisoner called five witnesses who gave him a good character.</p>
               <p>
